# extendedLogDataStringEncoding

**Instance Property**

The string encoding for the [doc://com.apple.mediaplayer/documentation/MediaPlayer/MPMovieAccessLog/extendedLogData] property.

## Declaration

```swift
var extendedLogDataStringEncoding: UInt { get }
```

## Discussion

For possible string encodings, see String_Encodings.

## Movie access log properties

- **extendedLogData**: A textual version of the web server access log for the associated movie player.
- **events**: The events in the movie access log.
